175
00:13:20,273 --> 00:13:21,316
<i>Chicago, Illinois, 9,2 Juta Jiwa</i>

176
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:23,152
Bisa dengar aku?

177
00:13:23,235 --> 00:13:25,905
